    "name": "Hunter Domain Search API",
    "description": "Returns all email addresses found on the internet using a given domain name or company name, along with sources for each, confidence scores, departments, seniority levels, and verification status. The Domain Search is Hunter's flagship endpoint and powers the public domain search tool on hunter.io.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Hunter Support",
